==名人堂==
2003年1月7日，卡特和[[艾迪·莫瑞|艾迪·莫瑞]]一同入選名人堂。卡特也成為博覽會隊史第一位名人堂選手。同年博覽會也將他的8號球衣退休。

2001年，卡特入選大都會名人堂。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newyork.mets.mlb.com/nym/history/nym_history_halloffame.jsp|title=Mets Hall of Fame|accessdate=July 27, 2009}}</ref>儘管大都會沒有正式退休他的背號8號，不過到目前為止仍未讓其他球員使用。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Steinberg |first1=Dan |title=Nats unveil Ring of Honor |url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/dcsportsbog/2010/08/nats_unveil_ring_of_honor.html |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |accessdate=August 14, 2018 |date=August 9, 2010}}</ref>
這年他與Dave McKay一同入選加拿大棒球名人堂。

==個人生活==
卡特在1975年結婚，並育有3名子女。<ref name="SI-Verducci-memory">{{cite news
 | last = Verducci
 | first = Tom
 | authorlink = Tom Verducci
 | title = Gary Carter, the light of the Mets
 | work = Sports Illustrated
 | publisher = Turner Broadcasting System
 | date = February 16, 2012
 | url = https://www.si.com/more-sports/2012/02/16/gary-carterobit
 | accessdate = April 9, 2019 }}</ref>他的女兒Kimmy曾是大學壘球隊教練。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pba.edu/media/news-releases/carter-baseball.cfm|title=Hall-of-Fame Catcher Gary Carter to Lead Sailfish Baseball|accessdate=October 13, 2009}}</ref>

2011年5月，卡特的腦部長了4顆惡性腫瘤。後來醫生證實他罹患了膠質母細胞瘤，而且已經無法根治。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2011/05/21/gary-carter-diagnosed-with-small-tumors-on-his-brain/|title=Gary Carter diagnosed with small tumors on his brain|accessdate=May 21, 2011|date=May 21, 2011|author=D.J. Short}}{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/2011/05/27/2011-05-27_doctors_tell_new_york_mets_great_gary_carter_that_brain_tumors_are_likely_malign.html|title=Doctors tell New York Mets great Gary Carter that brain tumors are likely malignant|accessdate=May 27, 2011|date=May 27, 2011|author=Bill Madden|work=Daily News}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/news/story?id=6613002|title=Gary Carter has glioblastoma|publisher=sports.espn.go.com|date=June 1, 2011}}</ref>為了進行治療，他也因此無法趕上他指導的大學棒球隊開幕戰。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/story/_/id/7536670/battling-brain-cancer-former-new-york-mets-catcher-gary-carter-makes-opener|title=Gary Carter makes team's opener|accessdate=February 3, 2012|date=February 3, 2012}}</ref>

2012年2月16日，卡特因病去世，享年57歲。<ref name="ESPNNewYork">{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/7583267/hall-fame-catcher-gary-carter-dies-age-57|title=Gary Carter Dies at 57|date=February 17, 2012|work=ESPNNewYork.com}}</ref>2014年3月28日，在藍鳥隊與大都會於蒙特婁舉辦的比賽賽前，大聯盟舉辦了紀念卡特的活動，並由卡特的遺孀和他女兒出席。<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.thestar.com/sports/bluejays/2014/03/28/tears_flow_at_big_o_as_former_expo_gary_carter_fondly_remembered.bb.html | title=Tears flow at Big O as former Expo Gary Carter fondly remembered | location=Toronto | work=The Star}}</ref>

